title: 66-50 THROUGH THE BIBLE REVELATION 22 by BRETT MEADOR September
description:
What is heaven? Be part of our study through Revelation 22 as we complete this round through the Bible.
See the pure river of water of life, and the tree of life that bears fruit for healing. There will be no more curse, no darkness. But God. See His face; He is Light.
He is Alpha and Omega. We get to be blessed in keeping the sayings of prophecy in this book! Herein we rest, in the grace of our Lord Jesus Christ.
